Titles.jpn: たべっ子どうぶつ THE MOVIE

Summaries.eng: The Tabekko Doubutsu are raining down from the sky! But if you look closely, the animals are all showing off their individual personalities — and their zero combat strength and zero tension… Can Lion and the other really save the world?! Expect an exciting, heart-pounting,  grand adventure that will keep you on the edge of your seat!
